### Risks and Mitigations

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|-----------|
| CSS variable values in theme data drift from `index.css` | Use `colors: null` for t3-light and t3-dark; only t3-midnight has explicit colors |
| Old localStorage value ("light"/"dark"/"system") breaks new hook | Migration logic in `getStored()` maps legacy values to new theme IDs |
| Inline `style.setProperty` not cleaned up when switching away from t3-midnight | `applyTheme` always clears all overrides before setting new ones (or when `colors` is null) |
| `color-scheme` not set, causing mismatched scrollbar colors | Explicitly set `color-scheme` in `applyTheme` |
| Tailwind `var(--color-*)` references not available in JS-applied values for t3-midnight | Use resolved OKLCH/hex values for t3-midnight colors, not Tailwind internal variables |
| `exactOptionalPropertyTypes: true` in tsconfig causes issues with optional `fontFamily`/`fontSize` | Define them with `| undefined` explicitly in the interface |

